---
<section class="bg-gray-50 py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6">
        Beyond Just a <span class="text-blue-600">Student Community</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
        We provide a platform for holistic growth through diverse technical and leadership initiatives.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 group text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-tight mb-2">Forums</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Weekly tech discussions & networking.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 group text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
           <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-tight mb-2">Workshops</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Hands-on technical skill building.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 group text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-orange-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
           <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-tight mb-2">Bootcamps</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Intensive learning tracks for developers.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 group text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-indigo-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
           <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.172 16.172a4 4 0 015.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-tight mb-2">Competitions</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Hackathons & coding challenges.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 group text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-50 text-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-purple-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
           <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M11 5.882V19.24a1.76 1.76 0 01-3.417.592l-2.147-6.15M18 13a3 3 0 100-6M5.436 13.683A4.001 4.001 0 017 6h1.832c4.1 0 7.625-1.234 9.168-3v14c-1.543-1.766-5.067-3-9.168-3H7a3.988 3.988 0 01-1.564-.317z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-tight mb-2">Campaigns</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Promoting tech awareness in Nepal.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
